@node Main "Chain_Gang - Documentation"

                            'Chain_Gang' 1.1

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Chain_Gang' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} where you move chainlinks so
they combine to make chains of 3 or more chainlinks of the same
colour, the more links there are in a chain, the more points you
get. Once a chain of 3 links (or more) is made, it is removed from
the board.

  Each time you move a chainlink and it doesn't complete a chain of
at least 3 chainlinks, three more chainlinks are added on the game
board... but do not let the game board fill up completely, because
when that happens, the game is over.

  As you progress in the game, nonmovable chainlinks, blocks
(movable or unmovable) or bombs may appear on the game board.

  Have fun!

